&lt;p&gt;  那就打开网站源代码看看，发现了底下有线索cat=dog&lt;a href=&#34;https://sm.ms/image/X38dLsJ5hSqG9QU&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/11/14/X38dLsJ5hSqG9QU.png&#34; &gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
